Insider Activity


Individual




Beatriz R. Perez



Ms. Beatriz R. Perez is Chief Public Affairs & Communications Officer at The Coca-Cola Co. and a Member at Victory Junction Gang Camp, Inc. She is on the Board of Directors at Hispanic Scholarship Fund, Primerica, Inc., The GRAMMY Foundation, USO, Inc. and Save The Children Federation, Inc. Ms. Perez was previously employed as a Member by Children's Healthcare of Atlanta, Inc. and Chief Marketing Officer by Coca-Cola North America. She also served on the board at Household Bank (Nevada) NA, HSBC Finance Corp. and HSBC North America Holdings, Inc. She received her undergraduate degree from the University of Maryland.



